<h1>About Winnipeg Tree Explorer</h1>

<p>
  This application uses the City of Winnipeg Tree Inventory dataset.
  The data includes individual trees, their botanical and common names,
  their neighbourhoods, and site/location information.
</p>

<p>
  The database is organized into three related tables:
  neighbourhoods, sites, and trees.
</p>

<p>
  A neighbourhood has many sites, and a site has many trees.
</p>